OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FVariable cloud with
OL,6,Fscattered mostly light showers and
OL,7,Fbright spells, A brisk breeze but
OL,8,Ffeeling warmer.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FThursday, cloudy start turning
OL,12,Fbrighter and warmer. Friday, sunny and
OL,13,Fvery warm, locally hot. Chance of
OL,14,Fthundery evening showers. Saturday,
OL,15,Fvery warm with bright spells, thundery
OL,16,Fshowers still possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
